description: Demolition of the existing building (Use Class E) and the comprehensive redevelopment of the site to provide a single tall building (205m AOD to the top of the building and 230m AOD to the top of the spire) providing residential accommodation (Use Class C3) along with a mix of flexible commercial uses (Use Class E) at ground floor level with associated hard and soft landscaping including the delivery of a new pocket park providing general public realm improvements.The Application is accompanied by an Environmental Impact Assessment.
site_name: Ensign House, 17 Admirals Way, Isle of Dogs, London, E14 9XQ
